00:04:07.270 --> 00:04:13.270
Alright, again, Dobryden, Priemno, Posna Jomitisa.

00:04:13.270 --> 00:04:19.269
Well, I still need to work on my accents, but I think you get the idea.

00:04:19.269 --> 00:04:28.269
With a little practice, you can ask simple questions and even introduce and explain a scripture.

00:04:28.269 --> 00:04:30.269
It really works.

00:04:30.269 --> 00:04:32.269
Let's look at an example.

00:04:32.269 --> 00:04:35.269
Hi there, we're making brief visits on our neighbor.

00:04:35.269 --> 00:04:37.269
Oh, Arabic?

00:04:37.269 --> 00:04:38.269
Yes.

00:04:38.269 --> 00:04:39.269
What's your name?

00:04:39.269 --> 00:04:40.269
My name is Abba.

00:04:40.269 --> 00:04:41.269
My name is Abba.

00:04:41.269 --> 00:04:43.269
Did you speak Arabic in Arabic?

00:04:43.269 --> 00:04:44.269
Yes.

00:04:44.269 --> 00:04:45.269
What?

00:04:45.269 --> 00:04:55.269
I've taught you a great way to give a witness to even more in our territory.

00:04:55.269 --> 00:05:01.269
Now, if mastering a whole presentation in another language seems a bit overwhelming,

00:05:01.269 --> 00:05:03.269
then here's a simple suggestion.

00:05:03.269 --> 00:05:05.269
Just learn a greeting.

00:05:05.269 --> 00:05:15.269
It's only a few words, but don't underestimate the power of greeting someone in their native tongue and with a warm smile.

00:05:15.269 --> 00:05:23.269
It can certainly open up doors, and it could also pave the way for you to call back with someone who does speak their language.

00:05:23.269 --> 00:05:27.269
And that brings us on to our third tip.

00:05:27.269 --> 00:05:30.269
Be diligent and follow up.

00:05:30.269 --> 00:05:39.269
Which, first of all, means trying to contact all those who weren't home initially, either on a different day or at a different time.

00:05:39.269 --> 00:05:46.269
And if you can't find them in that way, then don't overlook letter writing and telephone witnessing.

00:05:46.269 --> 00:05:50.269
These methods prove very effective during the pandemic.

00:05:50.269 --> 00:05:55.269
And even now, they can still help us to reach those we can't find at home.

00:05:55.269 --> 00:05:59.269
Regardless of what way we have contacted someone,

00:05:59.269 --> 00:06:08.269
please be sure not to forget them, but return promptly to follow up on any interest that you have found.

00:06:08.269 --> 00:06:13.269
You know, reaching everyone in our territory is definitely a challenge.

00:06:13.269 --> 00:06:26.269
But the tips we've discussed here today, one being observant, two being prepared, and three being diligent as we follow up on interest that we find,

00:06:26.269 --> 00:06:31.269
can help all of us fully accomplish our ministry.

00:06:31.269 --> 00:06:41.269
If we do that, we'll be imitating Jesus, who wanted to give everyone an opportunity to come to know Jehovah.
